the vengeful flames of a thousand suns.

04:06.031 --> 04:09.200
You shall curse your mothers
for the day of your birth.

04:09.367 --> 04:11.620
So go now. Go!

04:11.787 --> 04:14.165
And begin your life of fear...

04:14.332 --> 04:17.000
...knowing that,
when you least expect it...

04:17.168 --> 04:21.298
...the looming sword of Damocles
will crash down upon you...

04:21.466 --> 04:23.259
